							<Data><![CDATA[The package type decides the behaviour of the production.           The usage type decides in which setting the program will run. Scroll - responsive production for both mobile and desktop. Includes building blocks for self-studies and individual activities. Slide - for a scalable production, mainly for desktop. Includes building blocks for group workshop activitites. Site - for creating a Title Site or a standard web page. All Scroll-blocks will be available. Mixed type - Use for invitation emails, promotional videos and other material. ]]></Data>
